===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Some kind of [[divine]] or [[supernatural]] aid, or reward.
# A pronouncement invoking divine aid.
# Good fortune.
# {{context|paganism}} A modern pagan ceremony.
# the act of declaring, seeking or bestowing favor
# a thing one is glad of

